How good there exist full-moon
nights, so we can traverse them.

307
00:38:15,059 --> 00:38:17,323
What would I do without
Lorenzo Rafael?

308
00:38:42,186 --> 00:38:44,586
Do you love me so much,
Lorenzo Rafael?

309
