00:47:56,106 --> 00:47:57,368
You are not well.

416
00:47:58,342 --> 00:47:59,536
I can see it in your eyes.

417
00:48:01,078 --> 00:48:03,569
Get some medicine,
rub on the body.

418
00:48:03,604 --> 00:48:05,691
If you are not
well until tomorrow,

419
00:48:05,726 --> 00:48:07,778
I will bring a shaman
to heal you.

420
00:48:08,018 --> 00:48:08,677
It is OK.

421
00:48:09,686 --> 00:48:11,210
Do not worry about me.

422
00:48:12,177 --> 00:48:14,094
And take care of yourself,
Lorenzo Rafael.

423
00:49:47,250 --> 00:49:48,717
Jesus, Maria, José.

