00:50:53,116 --> 00:50:55,141
It was Mr. Damian, no one but him.

428
00:50:56,920 --> 00:50:58,444
But since he is the boss,

429
00:50:58,789 --> 00:50:59,653
they can do it.

430
00:51:14,104 --> 00:51:15,071
What happened?

431
