00:54:02,772 --> 00:54:06,071
Take it, and tell mr. Damian that
Maria Candelária owes him nothing.

466
00:54:28,765 --> 00:54:31,598
- Who is it?
- It me, José Afonso.

467
00:54:38,875 --> 00:54:40,570
Why did you accept the pig?

468
00:54:40,977 --> 00:54:43,946
