it did not come with good intentions.

469
00:54:43,981 --> 00:54:46,515
- What should I do with it?
- Bury it.

470
00:54:47,150 --> 00:54:49,118
Dogs can get sick.

471
00:54:49,519 --> 00:54:50,508
Wait.

472
00:54:52,255 --> 00:54:54,223
I will close the store
for a few days.

473
